&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Perform rigorous analysis&lt;/strong&gt;: Apply calculations, finite element analysis (FEA), and trade studies to guide design decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive validation &amp;amp; reliability&lt;/strong&gt;: Lead prototyping, testing, and root cause analysis to ensure robust, reliable hardware.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pursue cost-down&lt;/strong&gt;: Identify and implement design and manufacturing approaches that reduce cost without sacrificing performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally&lt;/strong&gt;: Define system requirements, lead design reviews, and integrate feedback across teams.&lt;/li&gt;
