&lt;p&gt;Antora is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Controls &amp;amp; Software Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to own the integration of the control systems and software that power our Thermal Energy Storage (TES) modules, industrial boilers, and complex balance-of-plant (BoP) systems.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a high-impact, site-based role for an engineer who thrives at the intersection of physical hardware and digital logic. You won&#39;t just be maintaining legacy systems; you will be architecting the brain of a first-of-a-kind energy technology. We are looking for a start up mindset &amp;nbsp;who leverages modern tools to accelerate traditional industrial automation workflows, using AI to streamline code generation, automate documentation, and rapidly troubleshoot complex system behaviors.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This role is strongly preferred to be located full time in San Jose, California but open but, &lt;em&gt;remote considered with 25% travel&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
