&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Establish best practices:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop and maintain CAD standards, documentation, and engineering infrastructure that support high-quality execution and scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mentor &amp;amp; lead:&lt;/strong&gt; Guide junior engineers and serve as a technical lead.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shape our processes:&lt;/strong&gt; Balance fast execution with long-term improvements in team workflows, risk management, and product development culture.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
