&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Execute TPV cell and module characterization at Antora’s TPV R&amp;amp;D and manufacturing facility. After training, independently perform photovoltaic cell and module characterization and reliability testing, generating the data that drives TPV R&amp;amp;D, reliability, and manufacturing operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
