&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years experience working in technical labs and/or production environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years experience with the characterization of electronic or optoelectronic devices.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience handling scientific samples; strong attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School Diploma, GED, or equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliability, strong work ethic, and a desire to learn.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort engaging with problems you haven’t encountered before.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent oral and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
